  <brief_title>Impact of an Integrated Intervention on Mental Health in Survivors of Intimate Partner Violence</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomised Controlled Trial of an Integrated Intervention on Mental Health in Survivors of Intimate Partner Violence</official_title>
